      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To require the Secretary of Housing and Urban Development to establish a process for incorporating transportation costs associated with the location of housing into affordability measures and standards, and to develop a transportation affordability index to measure and disclose the transportation costs associated with the location of a home.</title>
